text: Ishenbai Duyshonbiyevich Kadyrbekov () (born July 16, 1949) is a Kyrgyzstani politician. He was the Chairman of the Legislative Assembly of Kyrgyzstan and the interim President in March 2005. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Kyrgyzstan
title: Ishenbai Kadyrbekov
